# Test Case Re-Run Policy

- If the user asks to "re-run", "rerun", or run a test case again, you MUST execute the test case fully from the beginning.
- NEVER skip or bypass the execution of a test case simply because it has previously passed or because there are existing test results/logs indicating a success.
- A request to run or re-run is an explicit instruction to perform the automation steps again in the browser.
